          "correct": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "mcq",
          "q": "3. What is the default STP priority for a Cisco switch?",
          "options": ["A. 4096", "B. 1", "C. 32768", "D. 65535"],
          "correct": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "mcq",
          "q": "4. A network administrator wants Switch3 to be the root bridge. Which command would achieve this with the highest certainty?",
          "options": ["A. spanning-tree vlan 1 priority 0", "B. spanning-tree vlan 1 priority 4096", "C. spanning-tree vlan 1 root primary", "D. Both A and C are effective, but A is more specific."],
          "correct": 3
        },
        {
          "type": "mcq",
          "q": "5. What is the first step in the Spanning Tree operation?",
